(8, 1, '2014-05-12 15:05:27', '2014-05-12 15:05:27', 'Wizard Technology is a brand new start-up, and although there is lots of experience from previous roles it''d be great to share with you <a href="http://wizard.technology/more-work/" title="More work">here</a>, it would be wrong to show these projects publicly. If you''d like to see more of the types of projects built (solely or been a part of) Please click <a href="mailto:info@wizard.technology?subject=View-Projects">here</a>.', 'Work', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'work', '', '', '2014-05-21 06:48:15', '2014-05-21 06:48:15', '', 0, 'http://wizard.technology/?page_id=8', 2, 'page', '', 0),
