(1713, 1, '2014-05-28 08:45:08', '2014-05-28 08:45:08', '<div class="services-break"></div>\r\n<section style="grid grid-pad">\r\n	<aside class="services-col col-1-3">\r\n		<div class="service-icon">\r\n			<div class="icon-inner"><img src="http://wizard.technology/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/build-maintenance-300x300.png" alt="build-maintenance" /></div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<p class="services-copy">Looking to increase your web presence? We specialise in the build and maintenance of websites and apps designed to drive more traffic for our clients. Each and every client has differing requirements. We can create completely bespoke implementations, tailored, ''off the shelf'' builds or anywhere in between to suit most budgets. </p>\r\n	</aside>\r\n	<aside class="services-col col-1-3">\r\n		<div class="service-icon">\r\n			<div class="icon-inner"><img src="http://wizard.technology/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/devices1-300x300.png" alt="devices" /></div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<p class="services-copy">Your websites and apps can be built to embrace the contemporary internet user''s needs, they may visit you on a range of devices such as desktop and tablet computers, or on their smartphone. We operate in a massively wide field, and we don''t claim to be the best in all areas. Instead we include a network of proven professionals to achieve a better end product.</p>\r\n	</aside>\r\n	<aside class="services-col col-1-3">\r\n		<div class="service-icon">\r\n			<div class="icon-inner"><img src="http://wizard.technology/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/communication-300x300.png" alt="communication" /></div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<p class="services-copy">We believe our expertise in selection and implementation of the appropriate technology to meet evolving requirements. We embrace change as being necessary to achieve the best possible results. We can discuss with you what you''d like to achieve (define your problem), and work with closely with you devise a solution to it, and then we''ll implement the solution. Then we can monitor feedback and adjust as necessary.</p>\r\n	</aside>\r\n</section>', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '6-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-28 08:45:08', '2014-05-28 08:45:08', '', 6, 'http://wizard.technology/6-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
